com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.reactor

Class ContinuousReactorBulkExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.api.AbstractBulkExecutor
      • com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.reactor.DefaultReactorBulkExecutor
        • com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.reactor.ContinuousReactorBulkExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsyncBulkExecutor, BulkExecutor, ReactiveBulkExecutor, AsyncBulkReader, BulkReader, ReactiveBulkReader, SyncBulkReader, SyncBulkExecutor, AsyncBulkWriter, BulkWriter, ReactiveBulkWriter, SyncBulkWriter, ReactorBulkExecutor, ReactorBulkReader, ReactorBulkWriter, AutoCloseable

    public class ContinuousReactorBulkExecutor
extends DefaultReactorBulkExecutor
implements ReactorBulkExecutor
    An implementation of BulkExecutor using Reactor, that executes all reads using continuous paging. This executor can achieve significant performance improvements for reads, provided that the read statements to be executed can be properly routed to a replica.
